long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This browser extension serves as a frontend for the SNH Titan by Freezingdata GmbH. It detects profiles, groups and more objects in various social networks. You can register the extension with a specific SNH2 installation (Desktop or Enterprise) and collect data with the click of a button.

Important: An activated SNH Titan installation is required on your machine or in your internal network.
